	(text "ReefVolt SensorBuddy\nTop-Level Sheet\n\nESP32-S3-MINI-1-N8: WiFi/BLE bridge, OLED, USB\nSTM32G0B1KBU6: Sensor coprocessor, FDCAN master\nTCAN1044VDRQ1: CAN bus transceiver\nUSBLC6-4SC6: USB ESD protection\n\nInter-MCU: USART1 (PA8/PA9 ↔ ESP32 GPIO)\nESP32 controls STM32 BOOT0 + NRST for in-system flashing"
